<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Git - 标签 - YYT6801's Blog</title><link>https://blog.yyt6801.top/tags/git/</link><description>YYT6801's Blog</description><generator>Hugo 0.139.2 &amp; FixIt v0.3.15</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>yyt6801@gmail.com (YYT6801)</managingEditor><webMaster>yyt6801@gmail.com (YYT6801)</webMaster><copyright>YYT6801</copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.yyt6801.top/tags/git/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Git常用操作</title><link>https://blog.yyt6801.top/posts/git-common-operations/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Dec 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>yyt6801@gmail.com (YYT6801)</author><guid>https://blog.yyt6801.top/posts/git-common-operations/</guid><category domain="https://blog.yyt6801.top/categories/programming-and-development/">Programming and Development</category><description>&lt;h2 id="将远程仓库的代码克隆到本地" class="heading-element">&lt;span>将远程仓库的代码克隆到本地&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%b0%86%e8%bf%9c%e7%a8%8b%e4%bb%93%e5%ba%93%e7%9a%84%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%81%e5%85%8b%e9%9a%86%e5%88%b0%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>在本地新建文件夹，进入文件夹内；&lt;/li>
&lt;li>在文件夹内打开git bash终端，使用 &lt;em>&lt;code>git clone url&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 命令把远程仓库的克隆到本地.例如将github上的某仓库克隆到本地:
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git clone https://github.com/yyt6801/for-my-dream.git&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="本地修改后同步到远程仓库" class="heading-element">&lt;span>本地修改后同步到远程仓库：&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e4%bf%ae%e6%94%b9%e5%90%8e%e5%90%8c%e6%ad%a5%e5%88%b0%e8%bf%9c%e7%a8%8b%e4%bb%93%e5%ba%93" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>查看本地仓库状态
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git status&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>把本地新增的文件添加到缓存区
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git add . &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>查看是否已存放至暂存区
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git status&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用 &lt;em>&lt;code>git add .&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 命令是将想要快照的内容写入缓存区中， 通过进一步执行 &lt;em>&lt;code>git commit&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 命令是将缓存区的内容添加到本地仓库中
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git commit –m &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;changes&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>把本地仓库代码推送到远程仓库
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git push&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="将本地仓库与远程仓库同步" class="heading-element">&lt;span>将本地仓库与远程仓库同步：&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%b0%86%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e4%bb%93%e5%ba%93%e4%b8%8e%e8%bf%9c%e7%a8%8b%e4%bb%93%e5%ba%93%e5%90%8c%e6%ad%a5" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>方法一：
在本地仓库获取最新的代码，检查所有更新，但并未改动本地仓库的代码。
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git fetch&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;strong>将远程仓库的代码合并到本地仓库中：执行 &lt;em>&lt;code>git merge&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 命令才会更新本地仓库的代码为最新。&lt;/strong> 至此，修改全部结束。
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git merge origin/master&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>方法二：
直接 &lt;em>&lt;code>git pull&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 即可实现同步。(拉取远程仓库最新的代码到本地仓库，相当于 &lt;em>&lt;code>git fetch + git merge&lt;/code>&lt;/em> )
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-Bash" data-lang="Bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git pull&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="取消本地修改内容" class="heading-element">&lt;span>取消本地修改内容&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%8f%96%e6%b6%88%e6%9c%ac%e5%9c%b0%e4%bf%ae%e6%94%b9%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>执行 &lt;em>&lt;code>git checkout -- filename&lt;/code>&lt;/em> 命令可以对某个文件撤销修改的内容。filename填写需要撤销修改的文件名(需包含路径)，&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>